2
00:00:46,020 --> 00:00:47,850
# We're reindeer, we're not horses #
# 我们是驯鹿 我们不是马 #

3
00:00:47,930 --> 00:00:50,160
# We're Santa's Flying Forces! Ho ho! #
# 我们是耶诞老人的飞行团队! 后后! #

4
00:00:51,760 --> 00:00:53,390
Hut! Hut! Hut! Hut!
小屋! 小屋! 小屋! 小屋!

5
00:00:53,460 --> 00:00:54,800
Hey!
喂!

6
00:00:56,500 --> 00:01:00,130
Guys! Guys! We lost Santa!
小伙子! 小伙子! 我们把耶诞老人弄丢了!

7
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:01,300
That's better.
那更好

8
00:01:02,070 --> 00:01:03,600
Julius, look!
朱利尔斯 你看!

9
00:01:03,670 --> 00:01:05,270
It's Santa's Flying Forces!
它是耶诞老人的飞行团队!

10
00:01:05,340 --> 00:01:07,740
- Not again!  - Yahoo!
- 又来了!  - 呀吼!

11
00:01:07,810 --> 00:01:10,440
Oh, Niko! Be careful!
阿 尼科! 小心!

12
00:01:10,520 --> 00:01:14,110
Whoa, whoa! Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!
噢 噢! 噢 噢 噢 噢!

13
00:01:14,190 --> 00:01:15,480
Whoa, whoa!
噢 噢!

14
00:01:23,430 --> 00:01:25,090
Niko, look out!
尼科 注意!

15
00:01:27,330 --> 00:01:28,820
Darn kid!
臭小子!

16
00:01:52,460 --> 00:01:54,550
I think I know which one my dad is.
我认为我知道哪一个是我的爸爸

17
00:01:54,630 --> 00:01:55,820
Don't tell me...
不要告诉我...

18
00:01:55,890 --> 00:01:58,290
the one who flies the fastest, jumps the highest,
那个飞最快的人 跳最高的人

19
00:01:58,360 --> 00:01:59,850
and has the most courage?
还是最勇敢的?

20
00:01:59,930 --> 00:02:01,360
Did you see him too?
你也看见他了吗?

21
00:02:02,870 --> 00:02:06,000
I'd do anything to be up there flying with my dad.
要是能与我的爸爸一起飞我愿意做任何事情

22
00:02:06,070 --> 00:02:07,730
I know, I know.
我知道 我知道

23
00:02:07,810 --> 00:02:12,270
But these things don't happen overnight. They take practice.
但是这些事情不可能一夜发生 他需要苦练

24
00:02:12,340 --> 00:02:14,070
But I'm always practicing!
但是我总是在练习ㄚ!

25
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:17,440
Sure, but you gotta really believe in yourself.
当然 但是你必须真的相信你自己

26
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,540
Huh?
嗯?

27
00:02:21,820 --> 00:02:23,810
I believe you can fly.
我相信你能飞

28
00:02:23,890 --> 00:02:26,120
Now show me that you believe it.
现下让我看看你相信

29
00:02:26,190 --> 00:02:28,850
That's my boy!
好样的!

30
00:02:28,930 --> 00:02:31,160
Don't think, believe!
不要乱想 要相信自己!

31
00:02:31,230 --> 00:02:34,860
Believe! Believe!
自信! 自信!

32
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:41,370
I don't believe it.
看来是我期望太高了

33
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:44,930
I almost flew this time, didn't I, Julius?
我几乎这次能飞 不是吗 朱利尔斯?

34
00:02:45,010 --> 00:02:46,500
You sure did, Niko.
你当然能做 尼科

35
00:02:46,580 --> 00:02:48,670
You sure did.
你当然能做

36
00:02:48,750 --> 00:02:51,270
Hey, Niko...
嗨 尼科...

37
00:02:51,350 --> 00:02:53,440
...was your daddy a chicken?
...你的爸爸是一支鸡吗?

38
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:56,280
'Cause you fly like a chicken!
因为你飞起来就像一支鸡!

39
00:02:56,350 --> 00:02:58,480
My dad's on the Flying Forces!
我的爸爸是飞行团队的!

40
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:02,010
Yeah, and my dad's Santa Claus.
是的 我爸爸还是耶诞老人勒

41
00:03:02,090 --> 00:03:03,620
Just you wait, or I'll...!
你等着瞧 否则我将...!

42
00:03:05,300 --> 00:03:07,490
Remember how we deal with bullies?
还记得我们怎样对付混混的吗?

43
00:03:07,570 --> 00:03:08,620
Chin up...
别灰心...

44
00:03:09,200 --> 00:03:11,260
...and just ignore them.
...别理他们

45
00:03:11,340 --> 00:03:14,070
My dad's a three-legged moose.
我的爸爸是一头三条腿的大角麋鹿

46
00:03:14,140 --> 00:03:17,940
Yeah! And my daddy's a four-headed... ugh!
是! 以及我的爸爸 乃4支大角麋鹿之首... 喔!

47
00:03:18,010 --> 00:03:19,310
Ugh!
喔!

48
00:03:19,380 --> 00:03:21,000
Now, that's ignoring.
现在 这才叫不理它

49
00:03:35,260 --> 00:03:37,320
I don't get it, Julius.
我不明白 朱利尔斯

50
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:39,730
If Dad's really on the Flying Forces,
如果爸爸真的是飞行团队

51
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,860
why can't I fly like him?
我为什么不能像他一样飞翔?

52
00:03:41,930 --> 00:03:44,060
No one knows exactly why
没有人知道为什么

53
00:03:44,140 --> 00:03:47,200
Santa's Flying Forces have the gift of flight.
耶诞老人的飞行团队有飞行才能

54
00:03:48,610 --> 00:03:50,510
Maybe those boys are right.
或许那些男孩说的对

55
00:03:50,580 --> 00:03:53,700
Maybe my dad isn't one of the Flying Forces.
或许我爸爸不是飞行团队

56
00:03:53,780 --> 00:03:57,240
You're ten times as brave as those boys.
你比那些男孩勇敢10倍的

57
00:03:57,320 --> 00:04:00,110
Just... pretend they're not there.
只不过... 假装他们不存在

58
00:04:00,180 --> 00:04:02,280
- You're right, Julius.  - Thank you.
- 你说对了 朱利尔斯  - 谢谢

59
00:04:02,350 --> 00:04:06,050
I'll go practice flying at Antler's Hill, where they can't see me.
我要去鹿角的小山练习飞行 在那里他们就不能看见我

60
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:09,120
Hey! That's not what I said!
喂! 那可不是我说的!

61
00:04:09,190 --> 00:04:10,490
Come back here.
回来

62
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:14,620
If anyone heard you talking about going to Antler's Hill for flying practice!
如果有人听到你要去鹿角的小山 练习飞行那就糟了!

63
00:04:14,700 --> 00:04:17,190
Are you going to Antler's Hill for flying practice?
你要去鹿角的小山练习飞行吗?

64
00:04:17,270 --> 00:04:20,290
No! Definitely not! No way!
不! 当然不! 不可能!

65
00:04:20,370 --> 00:04:22,130
- Can I come along?  - Would you?
- 我能一块去吗?  - 好吗?

66
00:04:22,210 --> 00:04:25,330
No one is going anywhere for flying practice, least of all to...
任何人都不能到别处去练习飞行 尤其是去...

67
00:04:25,410 --> 00:04:26,880
Antler's Hill!
鹿角的小山!

68
00:04:26,940 --> 00:04:28,970
Antler's Hill?!
鹿角的小山吗?!

69
00:04:29,050 --> 00:04:31,640
How many times have you been told, Niko?
我告诉你多少次 尼科?

70
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:34,240
Sneaking out of Home Valley is strictly forbidden!
偷偷溜出家的山谷之外 是严格禁止的!

71
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:35,380
Yes, sir.
是的 先生

72
00:04:35,450 --> 00:04:37,750
Niko wasn't sneaking anywhere.
尼科没溜到任何地方

73
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:39,520
I asked him to come and help me...
我是要他来帮我...

74
00:04:39,590 --> 00:04:40,490
Huh?
嗯?

75
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:43,050
...pick up my Aunt Sally. She hasn't been well.
...接我的姑母萨莉 她身体不大好

76
00:04:43,130 --> 00:04:44,190
Aunt Sally!
萨莉姑母!

77
00:04:44,260 --> 00:04:45,190
Huh?
嗯?

78
00:04:45,260 --> 00:04:47,660
Everybody, this is my Aunt Sally.
大家好 这是我的姑母萨莉

79
00:04:51,170 --> 00:04:53,070
I'd better be going now.
大家好 我现在最好赶快走

80
00:04:53,140 --> 00:04:56,500
- I'll take you!  - Such a good boy!
- 我送给你!  - 真是个好男孩!

81
00:04:58,010 --> 00:04:59,440
Let me get that for you.
让我为你弄好

82
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:03,370
All right, all right.
好 好

83
00:05:03,450 --> 00:05:05,680
But it won't be so funny if the wolves see you.
如果让野狼看见你 它将不是如此有趣

84
00:05:05,750 --> 00:05:10,080
We're only safe here in the valley as long as the wolves don't know it exists.
我们只要在这山谷里是最安全的 只要野狼不知道它的存在

85
00:05:10,150 --> 00:05:13,150
That's why no one leaves Home Valley.
这就是没有人会离开山谷的原因

86
00:05:13,220 --> 00:05:15,060
- Yes, sir.  - Yes, Dad.
- 是的 先生  - 是的 爸爸

87
00:05:16,830 --> 00:05:18,320
You heard our leader.
你们听到我们领导人的话了

88
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:21,460
I don't want to hear any more talk of going to Antler's Hill.
我再也不想听到 谁要去鹿角的小山

89
00:05:21,530 --> 00:05:22,860
Is that clear?
清楚了吗?

90
00:05:22,930 --> 00:05:25,530
Okay, Julius.
好吧 朱利尔斯

91
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,870
Finally, I'm getting through to you.
终於 使你明白了

92
00:05:29,740 --> 00:05:31,970
See you tomorrow at Antler's Hill!
明天鹿角的小山见!

93
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:38,010
Now, let's see. I'm sure I was supposed to take a right back there,
现在 我们看看我确信 我们应该退回去右转

94
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:39,610
and then a left,
然后左边

95
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:42,620
and then another left, and then a right.
然后在左边 然后右边

96
00:05:42,690 --> 00:05:46,920
That means I should be back at the tourist bus right about...
那表示我们应该 在旅游巴士回到...

97
00:05:46,990 --> 00:05:48,290
now?
现在?

98
00:05:56,730 --> 00:05:58,790
Niko, stay still!
尼科 别动!

99
00:05:58,870 --> 00:06:03,310
Mom, why does nobody believe that Dad is one of the Flying Forces?
妈妈 为什么没人相信 爸爸是飞行团队的?

100
00:06:03,370 --> 00:06:07,280
Well, no one ever met him, apart from me.
嗯 从来没有人见过他 除了我之外

101
00:06:07,340 --> 00:06:09,210
Tell me about Dad again.
再给我说说爸爸的事

102
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:11,370
Okay.
好吧

103
00:06:11,450 --> 00:06:12,710
Ugh...
嗯...

104
00:06:12,780 --> 00:06:17,880
Your dad was the handsomest reindeer in Santa's Flying Forces.
你爸爸是耶诞老人飞行团队里 最漂亮的驯鹿

105
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:19,650
That must be where I get it.
这点我一定遗传了爸爸

106
00:06:21,030 --> 00:06:22,720
It was the day after Christmas,
那是在耶诞节之后日子

107
00:06:22,790 --> 00:06:25,790
and I went out on my own looking for moss.
我独自走出去 寻找苔藓

108
00:06:25,860 --> 00:06:30,030
Suddenly, the Flying Forces landed right in front of me.
突然 飞行团队 降落在我的面前

109
00:06:30,100 --> 00:06:32,830
Santa's sleigh had broken down.
耶诞老人的雪橇坏了

110
00:06:32,900 --> 00:06:34,530
And what happened then?
然后发生什么事?

111
00:06:34,610 --> 00:06:36,540
That's when I met your dad.
我就在那时遇见你爸爸

112
00:06:36,610 --> 00:06:38,940
He was a real daredevil,
他真是一位勇士

113
00:06:39,010 --> 00:06:42,740
and once he'd fixed the sleigh, he took me for a spin.
他把雪橇修好 带我去兜圈子

114
00:06:43,780 --> 00:06:45,010
It was magical!
太不可思议了!

115
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:48,180
Flying through the clouds high above the valley...
在高高山谷之间穿梭云间...

116
00:06:49,320 --> 00:06:50,810
... but then he had to leave.
...然而最后他必须离开

117
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:56,260
After that, I never saw him again.
在那之后 我从未再见到他

118
00:06:56,330 --> 00:06:58,560
If Daddy was so great,
如果爸爸如此伟大

119
00:06:58,630 --> 00:07:01,260
how come he never came to visit his son?
怎么从不来 看看他的儿子?

120
00:07:01,330 --> 00:07:06,130
Well, he never knew Niko here would be born that very next spring.
嗯 他不知道隔年 生了尼科

121
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:07,500
Who could know?
谁又能知道?

122
00:07:07,570 --> 00:07:09,630
But why didn't you go and tell him?
但是你为什么没去告诉他?

123
00:07:09,710 --> 00:07:13,370
Because he lives with the Flying Forces in Santa's Fell,
因为他和飞行团队住在 耶诞老人的家

124
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:15,610
and no one knows the way there.
没有人知道去的路

125
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:17,370
Don't you miss him?
你不想念他吗?

126
00:07:17,450 --> 00:07:22,940
No. I have one man in my life, and he's quite enough.
不在我的生命里有一个男人 有他就足够了

127
00:07:23,020 --> 00:07:24,890
Now, go to sleep, Niko.
现在 就寝罗尼科

128
00:07:26,660 --> 00:07:29,630
Mom, what's Dad's name?
妈妈 爸爸的名字叫什么?

129
00:07:29,690 --> 00:07:31,390
Good night, Niko.
晚安 尼科

130
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:52,910
More bad luck, boss.
更坏的运气 头家

131
00:07:52,980 --> 00:07:55,210
No reindeer anywhere.
任何地方都没有驯鹿

132
00:07:55,290 --> 00:07:58,310
We need reindeer.
我们需要驯鹿

133
00:07:58,390 --> 00:08:01,550
We need food.
我们需要食物

134
00:08:02,760 --> 00:08:04,280
I've got an idea, boss.
我有一种办法 头家

135
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:06,420
One word: moss.
一句话 苔藓

136
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:09,590
Huh? Huh? Huh?
嗯? 嗯? 嗯?

137
00:08:11,570 --> 00:08:15,100
Reindeer eat moss. We eat reindeer.
驯鹿吃苔藓我们吃驯鹿

138
00:08:15,170 --> 00:08:16,900
I'm simply cutting out the middleman.
仅去掉中间细节

139
00:08:18,110 --> 00:08:20,010
Please yourself.
随你便

140
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:22,440
Our luck must change.
我们必须改改运气

141
00:08:22,510 --> 00:08:25,410
Go out there, find food.
出去 找到食物

142
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:28,180
Find reindeer.
找到驯鹿

143
00:08:32,560 --> 00:08:33,580
Aah!
啊!

144
00:08:37,660 --> 00:08:39,130
Crash-landing maneuver.
迫降演习

145
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:41,100
Never know when you're gonna need it.
当你将要需要它时

146
00:08:41,170 --> 00:08:43,460
I thought I'd find you here.
我认为我将在这里找到你

147
00:08:43,530 --> 00:08:46,230
What do you have to say for yourself, young man?
你还有什么可解释的 年轻人?

148
00:08:46,300 --> 00:08:47,860
You've got to help me.
你必须帮助我

149
00:08:47,940 --> 00:08:50,630
I've been making a fool of myself all morning.
我整个上午都在当傻瓜

150
00:08:50,710 --> 00:08:53,370
None of that! It's dangerous out here!
少来! 这里很危险!

151
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:56,110
Straight back to Home Valley with you.
我得赶紧和你回到山谷

152
00:08:56,180 --> 00:08:57,440
Please?
求求你?

153
00:08:57,510 --> 00:09:00,310
Oh, all right.
噢 好

154
00:09:00,380 --> 00:09:01,820
But only for one minute.
但是只有一分钟

155
00:09:03,690 --> 00:09:06,950
Maybe you don't have to fly.
或许你不必飞

156
00:09:07,020 --> 00:09:09,320
Maybe you could glide.
或许你能滑动

157
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:12,520
It's really just falling, but slower.
只是坠落 但是更慢

158
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:15,000
Hey, I'm great at falling.
嘿 我擅长坠落

159
00:09:15,070 --> 00:09:18,130
Good! Now, climb to the top of that tree and...
好! 现在 爬到那树上...

160
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:20,930
Are you crazy? Reindeer don't climb trees.
你发疯吗? 驯鹿不爬树的

161
00:09:21,010 --> 00:09:22,230
That's just dumb.
那太愚蠢了

162
00:09:22,310 --> 00:09:24,500
Wow! Are you really going to do it?
哇! 你真的要那么做?

163
00:09:24,580 --> 00:09:28,440
Oh, yeah, and uh, don't try and stop me.
噢 是 噢 不要想办法停止我

164
00:09:35,350 --> 00:09:36,840
Not bad.
坏不坏

165
00:09:43,930 --> 00:09:46,090
Uh-huh!
噢!

166
00:09:46,160 --> 00:09:47,460
Uhh!
啊!

167
00:09:47,530 --> 00:09:50,300
Uhh... aaahhhh!
啊... 啊啊!

168
00:09:54,340 --> 00:09:56,570
Now, that's a view.
现在 好美的景色

169
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:58,570
Breathtaking.
美极了

170
00:09:58,640 --> 00:10:01,270
No wonder reindeer have been so hard to find.
难怪驯鹿 如此难发现

171
00:10:01,350 --> 00:10:03,070
What are you on about, Specs?
你说什么 史贝斯?

172
00:10:03,150 --> 00:10:04,810
They've started living in trees.
他们已经开始生活在树上了

173
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:06,370
Ugh.
啊

174
00:10:06,450 --> 00:10:07,680
What?
怎么了?

175
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:17,060
Don't worry, Niko. I know you'll fly one day.
不要担心 尼科 我知道你有一天将会飞

176
00:10:17,660 --> 00:10:18,820
Really?
真的吗?

177
00:10:18,900 --> 00:10:20,060
You think so?
你这样想吗?

178
00:10:20,130 --> 00:10:21,360
Sure.
当然

179
00:10:22,770 --> 00:10:24,560
Wo...! Wo...!
哦...! 哦...!

180
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:26,030
Wolves!
野狼!

181
00:10:27,170 --> 00:10:29,330
Run, kids!
快跑孩子们!

182
00:10:29,410 --> 00:10:30,960
Aaahhh!
啊啊!

183
00:10:44,050 --> 00:10:45,720
Oh, whoa!
噢 哼!

184
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:48,590
Aah aah aah!
啊 啊 啊!

185
00:10:50,090 --> 00:10:51,690
Nah nah-nah nah-nah!
呐 呐 呐 呐 呐!

186
00:10:57,230 --> 00:10:59,500
Look where you're going, boys.
看你将去哪儿 孩子们

187
00:10:59,570 --> 00:11:01,540
Ow! Guhh...
喔唷! 啊...

188
00:11:09,650 --> 00:11:11,580
They shouldn't be able to find our tracks now.
现在他们应该不能 找到我们的踪迹

189
00:11:16,490 --> 00:11:19,120
Come on, Saga. We've got to warn the herd.
跟我来 传奇 我们必须警告鹿群

190
00:11:27,800 --> 00:11:28,960
Wolves!
野狼!

191
00:11:29,030 --> 00:11:31,430
- Hey?  - Wolves! Wolves!
- 喂?  - 野狼! 野狼!

192
00:11:31,500 --> 00:11:34,440
- What's going on?  - Wolves! We saw them!
- 发生什么事?  - 野狼! 我们看见他们了!

193
00:11:34,510 --> 00:11:36,200
Niko, I thought I told you to...
尼科 我认为我告诉你了...

194
00:11:36,270 --> 00:11:38,240
Are you sure they didn't follow you?
你确信他们没跟踪你吗?

195
00:11:38,310 --> 00:11:41,110
Yes, Grandpa, we lost 'em.
是的 爷爷 我们甩掉他们了

196
00:11:41,180 --> 00:11:43,770
Are you absolutely certain?
你绝对肯定吗?

197
00:11:43,850 --> 00:11:46,320
Black Wolf will be pleased.
头家狼准高兴的

198
00:11:46,380 --> 00:11:48,440
Come on, Specs, let's eat!
来吧 史背 我们开吃!

199
00:11:48,520 --> 00:11:52,350
You go ahead. I'm stuffed. Just had some moss.
你继续 我好撑 刚吃了些苔藓

200
00:11:52,420 --> 00:11:54,250
Woohoooooo!
喔!

201
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,620
Ohhh!
哦!

202
00:11:55,690 --> 00:11:57,090
Defensive formation.
防御队形

203
00:11:57,160 --> 00:12:00,690
Men on the outside, women and children on the inside. Hurry!
男人在外面上女人小孩在里面 赶快!

204
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:02,630
Children! Stay together, children.
孩子们! 孩子们 待在一起

205
00:12:02,700 --> 00:12:04,430
Kids, stay close to your mothers.
孩子们 靠拢妈妈

206
00:12:05,540 --> 00:12:06,730
Children, together.
孩子们镇静

207
00:12:06,800 --> 00:12:09,470
Keep it moving! Come on! Keep it moving!
动起来! 跟我来! 动起来!

208
00:12:10,810 --> 00:12:13,470
Keep in! Keep in!
待里面! 待里面!

209
00:12:18,420 --> 00:12:20,180
Emergency evacuation!
紧急撤退!

210
00:12:20,250 --> 00:12:21,480
Run!
跑!

211
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:40,460
Dad!
爸爸!

212
00:12:40,540 --> 00:12:42,340
Come on! Hurry up!
跟来! 赶快!

213
00:12:58,390 --> 00:13:00,480
Dad! Come on!
爸爸! 跟我来!

214
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:07,190
Hey, you let 'em get away.
喂 你让他们跑了

215
00:13:17,540 --> 00:13:19,840
Niko! Thank goodness you're okay.
尼科! 谢天谢地你没事

216
00:13:21,550 --> 00:13:22,670
What's going on?
发生什么事?

217
00:13:24,050 --> 00:13:28,680
Everyone, stay calm.
每一人 保持镇静

218
00:13:29,890 --> 00:13:33,550
Who left the valley and led the wolves to us?
是谁离开山谷 引来野狼的?

219
00:13:35,890 --> 00:13:37,220
I...
我...

220
00:13:37,290 --> 00:13:39,490
I was sure they didn't follow us.
我确信他们没跟踪我们

221
00:13:39,560 --> 00:13:41,860
Flying practice again, was it?
又是飞行练习 是吗?

222
00:13:41,930 --> 00:13:45,870
Look what your silly dream has cost us...
看吧你的傻梦 已经带来我们恶梦...

223
00:13:45,940 --> 00:13:49,700
our home, and very nearly our lives.
我们的家 以及我们的生活

224
00:13:51,580 --> 00:13:52,740
That's enough!
够了!

225
00:13:52,810 --> 00:13:56,040
He's just a boy. He didn't mean for any of this to happen.
他只是一个孩子他也不想为这事发生

226
00:13:56,110 --> 00:13:57,340
Hmph.
哼

227
00:13:57,420 --> 00:13:59,540
The wolves will come back,
野狼将回来

228
00:13:59,620 --> 00:14:02,610
and when they do, there will be many.
他们来时 将会一整群

229
00:14:02,690 --> 00:14:05,750
We must keep moving.
我们必须继续走

230
00:14:07,220 --> 00:14:08,450
Oona is right.
乌纳是正确的

231
00:14:10,130 --> 00:14:11,720
We have to keep moving.
我们必须继续走

232
00:14:11,800 --> 00:14:15,860
Where to, I do not know.
到那里 我不知道

233
00:14:20,970 --> 00:14:24,930
I don't know what to do with the boy, Julius.
我不知道该拿这男孩怎么办 朱利尔斯

234
00:14:25,010 --> 00:14:27,310
He just doesn't listen.
他就是不听话

235
00:14:27,380 --> 00:14:29,440
He'll grow out of it, Miss Oona.
他长大就 乌纳小姐

236
00:14:29,510 --> 00:14:32,610
From now on, there will be no more mention of his father
今后 别再提到他父亲

237
00:14:32,680 --> 00:14:34,810
or of flying lessons.
或者飞行课

238
00:14:37,350 --> 00:14:40,020
He just has to forget all that.
他必须忘记所有

239
00:14:49,130 --> 00:14:51,230
That boy Niko is a jinx!
那个男孩尼科是个克星!

240
00:14:51,300 --> 00:14:53,600
Unreliable!
不可靠!

241
00:14:53,670 --> 00:14:56,800
How can you trust a boy who thinks he can fly?
你怎能相信认为他能飞的人?

242
00:15:01,010 --> 00:15:04,380
I know. If only I hadn't gone with Niko,
我知道 要是我没和尼科一起去该多好

243
00:15:04,450 --> 00:15:06,350
then we'd still have a home.
然后我们就不会失去家园

244
00:15:06,420 --> 00:15:09,510
I don't want you playing with Niko again.
我不想要你 再次和尼科玩了

245
00:15:09,590 --> 00:15:13,020
Next time he might bring death to us all.
下次 他可能把我们全部害到都死掉

246
00:15:37,110 --> 00:15:39,670
No wolves to be seen.
没有看见野狼

247
00:15:39,750 --> 00:15:40,980
Where's Niko?
尼科在那里?

248
00:15:41,050 --> 00:15:43,320
- Niko!  - Niko!
- 尼科!  - 尼科!

249
00:15:43,390 --> 00:15:44,850
- Niko!  - Niko!
- 尼科!  - 尼科!

250
00:15:44,920 --> 00:15:47,860
- Come on! Niko?  - Niko, where are you?
- 快点尼科?  - 尼科 你在那里?

251
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:50,650
- Niko's gone!  - Niko?
- 尼科已经走了!  - 尼科?

252
00:15:50,730 --> 00:15:52,390
We have to go back and find him.
我们必须回去找到他

253
00:15:52,460 --> 00:15:56,300
I'm sorry, Oona, but we must continue.
对不起 乌纳 但是我们必须继续走

254
00:15:56,370 --> 00:15:58,460
Otherwise, the wolves will track us down.
否则 野狼 将会追上我们

255
00:15:58,540 --> 00:16:01,130
Please, Dad, we have to find Niko.
求求你 爸爸 我们必须找到尼科

256
00:16:01,210 --> 00:16:03,070
I'm not leaving without my son.
找不到我儿子 我决不离开

257
00:16:03,140 --> 00:16:04,870
No one leaves the herd!
谁都不准离开鹿群!

258
00:16:04,940 --> 00:16:06,570
What if the wolves find your tracks?
如果野狼找到你的踪迹 怎么办?

259
00:16:06,640 --> 00:16:09,240
- But...  - You'll bring them down on us.
- 但是...  - 你会把狼群引来的

260
00:16:09,310 --> 00:16:11,300
We'll all die.
我们全部都会死

261
00:16:12,520 --> 00:16:13,980
He's right, Miss Oona.
他是对的 乌纳小姐

262
00:16:14,050 --> 00:16:15,710
This is a job for me.
这是我的工作

263
00:16:15,790 --> 00:16:17,880
I can avoid the wolves by flying
我能透过飞 来避开野狼

264
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:20,150
and spot the boy from the air.
能从空中找到他

265
00:16:21,630 --> 00:16:24,990
You must promise to bring him back, Julius.
你必须许诺 把他带回来 朱利尔斯

266
00:16:25,060 --> 00:16:27,160
Don't you worry about a thing.
你不必担心

267
00:16:36,910 --> 00:16:38,140
Niko!
尼科!

268
00:16:39,810 --> 00:16:41,210
Niko!
尼科!

269
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:50,590
Niko! Wait!
尼科! 等等!

270
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:55,750
Ah. So... where we going?
啊 因此... 我们要去哪?

271
00:16:55,830 --> 00:16:58,230
I'm going to Santa's Fell.
我要去耶诞老人的家

272
00:16:58,300 --> 00:17:01,700
I'm spending Christmas with my dad.
我要与我爸爸一起过耶诞节

273
00:17:01,770 --> 00:17:03,100
Great idea.
极妙的想法

274
00:17:03,170 --> 00:17:05,500
Really? You think so?
真的吗? 你这样想吗?

275
00:17:05,570 --> 00:17:07,830
Sure! Only...
当然! 只是...

276
00:17:07,910 --> 00:17:10,570
Well, there is one small detail.
嗯 有一个小的细节

277
00:17:10,640 --> 00:17:13,700
Nobody knows where Santa's Fell is.
没人知道耶诞老人的家在那

278
00:17:13,780 --> 00:17:18,540
So... why don't we go back to the herd and ask around,
因此... 我们为什么不回去鹿群那 打听一下

279
00:17:18,620 --> 00:17:20,680
and maybe someone might know.
或许某人知道

280
00:17:20,750 --> 00:17:22,380
I know where it is.
我知道它在那里

281
00:17:22,450 --> 00:17:23,720
Really?
真的?

282
00:17:23,790 --> 00:17:28,280
The Flying Forces always disappear behind that big fell on their way home...
飞行团队总是消失 在他们回家路上的大瀑布后面...

283
00:17:28,360 --> 00:17:30,830
Hey! So does the moon, big guy!
嘿! 月亮也是!

284
00:17:30,900 --> 00:17:33,960
...which means Santa's Fell must be on the other side of it.
...哪个表明耶诞老人的家一定 在它的另一边

285
00:17:34,030 --> 00:17:35,060
Nonsense!
胡说!

286
00:17:35,130 --> 00:17:37,190
I have to be strict with you, young man.
我必须对你严格了 年轻人

287
00:17:37,270 --> 00:17:41,470
I'm drawing this line here, and if you cross it...
我在这画条线 如果你跨过它...

288
00:17:42,670 --> 00:17:43,870
I will...
我将...

289
00:17:45,980 --> 00:17:49,170
Fine! But you're on your own, Niko.
好! 但是你是一个人 尼科

290
00:17:49,250 --> 00:17:50,910
I'm leaving.
我离开了

291
00:17:52,580 --> 00:17:53,950
You hear that?
你听到了吗?

292
00:17:54,690 --> 00:17:56,480
That's me, leaving.
那是我 要走了

293
00:17:56,550 --> 00:17:58,520
Leaving, leaving, leaving.
走了 走了 走了

294
00:17:58,590 --> 00:17:59,780
Good!
好!

295
00:17:59,860 --> 00:18:02,690
'Cause I'm a jinx, and I'm unreliable.
因我是个克星 并且我不可靠

296
00:18:02,760 --> 00:18:06,160
- Uhh...  - You're better off without me.
- 啊...  - 你离我远点 比较好

297
00:18:06,230 --> 00:18:08,130
Huh?
嗯?

298
00:18:08,200 --> 00:18:09,930
Oh.
噢

299
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:12,530
Then again... Santa's Fell?
然而... 耶诞老人的家吗?

300
00:18:12,600 --> 00:18:15,970
Are you kidding me? I've always wanted to go there.
你跟我开玩笑吗? 我总是想要去那里

301
00:18:16,040 --> 00:18:18,200
Lots of toys, right?
许多玩具 是吗?

302
00:18:19,040 --> 00:18:20,700
And elves!
以及小精灵!

303
00:18:20,780 --> 00:18:22,840
Who doesn't love elves?
谁不爱小精灵?

304
00:18:34,430 --> 00:18:35,980
Doggies!
小狗!

305
00:18:36,060 --> 00:18:37,460
I'm saved!
我得救了!

306
00:18:40,360 --> 00:18:44,560
How do you lose a whole herd of reindeer?
你怎会没看见一整群驯鹿?

307
00:18:44,640 --> 00:18:47,870
Those reindeer are meanies, boss.
那些驯鹿 太恶毒了 头家

308
00:18:47,940 --> 00:18:51,340
I mean, look at poor Smiley. They nearly crushed him to death.
我的意思是 看看可怜的笑脸符 他们差点把他整死了

309
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:55,410
What I need's a miracle with this lot!
与这批一起干活 需要奇迹!

310
00:18:55,480 --> 00:18:58,410
Oh, am I glad to see a friendly face.
噢 我好高兴 看见一张友好的脸

311
00:18:58,480 --> 00:18:59,310
Huh?
嗨?

312
00:18:59,380 --> 00:19:00,610
Hi! How do you do?
喂! 你好?

313
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:03,680
- I'm Essie. Nice to meet you.  - Wow!
- 我是埃西 很高兴见到你  - 哇!

314
00:19:03,750 --> 00:19:06,050
You would not believe what I've been through.
你将不相信我经历哪些事

315
00:19:06,120 --> 00:19:08,820
One minute I'm minding my own business while the owners go skiing,
一分钟我主人滑雪时 我还在考虑自己的事

316
00:19:08,890 --> 00:19:13,060
next minute it's like, Hello! Where are all the signs?
下分钟就好像 你好! 那些标志在那里?

317
00:19:13,130 --> 00:19:16,030
I must have been wandering around for days.
我一定是在外徘徊好几天了

318
00:19:16,100 --> 00:19:18,230
Be a sweetheart and fetch me some water.
作一个好人 为我拿一些水吧

319
00:19:18,300 --> 00:19:20,000
I am dry as a bone.
我都渴成骨头了

320
00:19:21,440 --> 00:19:25,100
Is he a little simple in the head?
他脑里头是否缺根筋?

321
00:19:26,310 --> 00:19:27,940
Poor pooch.
可怜的狗狗

322
00:19:29,810 --> 00:19:31,540
You're no pooch.
你不是狗狗

323
00:19:31,620 --> 00:19:34,020
You're... a wolf.
你是... 一匹野狼

324
00:19:34,080 --> 00:19:36,780
And you're a marshmallow,
而你是一颗小软糖

325
00:19:36,850 --> 00:19:39,150
sweet and tasty.
甜和可口

326
00:19:44,860 --> 00:19:46,960
# We're reindeer, we're not horses #
# 我们是驯鹿 我们不是马 #

327
00:19:47,030 --> 00:19:48,860
# We're Santa's Flying Forces! Ho ho! #
# 我们是耶诞老人的飞行团队! 后后! #

328
00:19:48,930 --> 00:19:51,870
I hate it when they do that!
当他们做那时 我憎恶它!

329
00:19:53,100 --> 00:19:56,230
But the Flying Forces are nice, and don't eat anyone.
但是飞行团队是好的 且不吃任何人

330
00:19:56,310 --> 00:19:59,240
They help Santa bring presents to all the children,
他们帮助耶诞老人帮孩子带来礼物

331
00:19:59,310 --> 00:20:01,610
and if you'd stop being naughty and become nice,
并且如果你将停止顽皮 且变成好的

332
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:04,440
Santa might give you a job too, and then...
耶诞老人也许可给你一个工作 然后...

333
00:20:04,520 --> 00:20:06,140
then you'll get plenty of food.
然后你将得到足够的食物

334
00:20:06,220 --> 00:20:08,880
Much better than eating me.
比吃我更好

335
00:20:08,950 --> 00:20:10,480
Right?
是吗?

336
00:20:12,360 --> 00:20:15,090
Flying Forces?
飞越团队吗?

337
00:20:15,160 --> 00:20:17,020
Santa Claus?
耶诞老人吗?

338
00:20:18,060 --> 00:20:19,460
Presents?
礼物吗?

339
00:20:20,460 --> 00:20:22,330
That's it.
就是这样

340
00:20:27,940 --> 00:20:29,960
Nobody touches the marshmallow.
谁也不行碰软糖

341
00:20:30,970 --> 00:20:33,200
She's given me an idea.
她已给我一种想法

342
00:20:33,280 --> 00:20:35,640
She's our lucky charm.
她是我们的吉祥物

343
00:20:37,850 --> 00:20:38,910
We're moving out.
我们要搬出去

344
00:20:38,980 --> 00:20:42,010
Next stop, Santa's Fell.
下一站 耶诞老人之家

345
00:20:48,260 --> 00:20:51,690
Let's... let's, uh, take a break, huh?
让我们... 这样 噢 休息一下 吗?

346
00:20:51,760 --> 00:20:53,350
Whew!
哎呀!

347
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:55,870
The Flying Forces!
飞行团队!

348
00:20:55,930 --> 00:20:58,770
We're almost there! Yes!
马上就到了! 耶!

349
00:21:00,770 --> 00:21:01,760
But...!
但是...!

350
00:21:16,220 --> 00:21:17,380
But...
但是...

351
00:21:17,450 --> 00:21:20,450
I was... so sure.
我是... 如此确信

352
00:21:20,520 --> 00:21:21,960
Whew.
嘘

353
00:21:22,030 --> 00:21:24,290
You did your best, Niko.
你尽力了 尼科

354
00:21:25,330 --> 00:21:27,350
At least you tried.
至少你试过了

355
00:21:27,430 --> 00:21:29,660
No one will ever be able to say we gave up.
没有人能说我们中途放弃了

356
00:21:31,940 --> 00:21:35,340
Hey! I thought we were giving up!
喂! 我认为我们放弃了!

357
00:21:51,050 --> 00:21:52,820
Almost!
差不多了!

358
00:21:56,160 --> 00:21:58,390
Whoo, yeah!
哇 耶!

359
00:21:59,400 --> 00:22:02,020
# Ain't no point in looking back #
# 后悔是没有意义的 #

360
00:22:02,100 --> 00:22:03,570
# So they tell me #
# 他们这样告诉我 #

361
00:22:03,630 --> 00:22:06,800
# Though I know this to be true #
# 虽然我知道这是真实的 #

362
00:22:06,870 --> 00:22:10,860
- # I've been tossing... #  - Are you... okay, madam?
- # 但我一直迟疑... #  - 你是... 好 夫人?

363
00:22:10,940 --> 00:22:12,740
Miss Wilma.
威尔玛小姐

364
00:22:12,810 --> 00:22:15,540
And, yes, I'm fine.
并且 是 我好的很

365
00:22:15,610 --> 00:22:17,340
But... you're trapped.
但是... 你被夹住了

366
00:22:17,410 --> 00:22:19,280
I'm not trapped!
我没被夹住!

367
00:22:19,350 --> 00:22:21,250
I'm just resting.
我只是在休息

368
00:22:21,320 --> 00:22:24,580
What?
哇?

369
00:22:26,960 --> 00:22:29,590
Whoa!
嗯!

370
00:22:30,590 --> 00:22:32,590
