喂! 我们刚刚救你的命!

372
00:22:35,130 --> 00:22:36,720
Exactly!
完全正确!

373
00:22:36,800 --> 00:22:40,830
Now I have to save both your lives before we're even.
在我们扯平之前 我也会救你们的命

374
00:22:40,910 --> 00:22:43,030
This is just great.
那太好了

375
00:22:43,110 --> 00:22:46,270
I'm already late for a big gig in the South.
对於在南方的一场大的爵士音乐会 已经赶不上了

376
00:22:46,340 --> 00:22:50,280
And you thought hanging upside down was going to speed things up?
你倒挂在树上 会使思考加速吗?

377
00:22:50,350 --> 00:22:53,910
Maybe I'll just have to save his life twice.
或许 我救他的命两次就行

378
00:22:56,390 --> 00:22:58,380
Don't worry, Wilma.
威尔玛 不要担心

379
00:22:58,460 --> 00:23:00,790
You don't have to save our lives.
你不必救我们俩的命

380
00:23:00,860 --> 00:23:02,350
We're heading north, anyway.
无论如何 我们要去北方

381
