That's north.
那才是北方

383
00:23:10,470 --> 00:23:11,700
Hmph!
哼!

384
00:23:13,500 --> 00:23:15,840
"That's west, Captain Compass.
"那是西方 罗盘船长

385
00:23:15,910 --> 00:23:17,370
That's north."
那才是北方 "

386
00:23:20,110 --> 00:23:21,810
Hmph!
哼!

387
00:23:23,980 --> 00:23:29,350
You know, Niko, that foolish weasel can teach you one important lesson:
知道吗 尼科 那支傻鼬 教你一门重要的课

388
00:23:29,420 --> 00:23:33,520
those who can't read nature will be beaten by nature.
不懂自然的人 最后将被大自然打败

389
00:23:33,590 --> 00:23:35,530
- Read?  - That's right.
- 是吗?  - 是的

390
00:23:35,590 --> 00:23:39,190
Take that cloud over there, for instance.
就拿那边的云 给你举例

391
00:23:39,260 --> 00:23:41,420
Now, what could that mean?
现在 那代表什么?

392
00:23:41,500 --> 00:23:43,660
That a storm is coming?
风暴雪将要来吗?

393
00:23:45,470 --> 00:23:47,730
A common mistake!
常识性错误!

394
00:23:47,810 --> 00:23:51,570
No, that particular type of cloud is harmless.
不 那种类型的云 无害的

395
00:23:51,640 --> 00:23:52,770
What it means is...
它的意思是...

396
00:23:52,840 --> 00:23:54,210
Uh!
噢!

397
00:23:54,280 --> 00:23:56,510
No need to be afraid, Niko!
没有需要害怕 尼科!

398
00:23:56,580 --> 00:23:58,510
It's just a gust!
只是一阵狂风!

399
00:24:01,290 --> 00:24:04,720
It'll blow over... before you know it!
我快被吹走了... 在你发现之前先告诉你!

400
00:24:04,790 --> 00:24:05,880
Ahh!
啊!

401
00:24:05,960 --> 00:24:06,790
Julius!
朱利尔斯!

402
00:24:08,690 --> 00:24:09,950
Julius!
朱利尔斯!

403
00:24:11,430 --> 00:24:13,060
Julius!
朱利尔斯!

404
00:24:18,970 --> 00:24:20,440
Julius!
朱利尔斯!

405
00:24:42,730 --> 00:24:47,190
I don't want to sound gushy or anything, but I just want you to know...
我不想显得很伤感或怎样 但我只想要你知道...

406
00:24:47,260 --> 00:24:49,060
Yes?
是吗?

407
00:24:49,130 --> 00:24:51,360
I would never eat you.
我绝不会吃你

408
00:24:52,040 --> 00:24:55,100
That's... sweet.
真是... 体贴ㄚ

409
00:24:55,170 --> 00:24:57,160
Yeah.
是ㄚ

410
00:25:08,150 --> 00:25:09,450
I'm hungry!
我饿死了!

411
00:25:09,520 --> 00:25:11,350
And I'm sick and tired of walking!
我累的不想走了!

412
00:25:15,060 --> 00:25:16,550
Listen up, men.
听着 老兄

413
00:25:16,630 --> 00:25:21,620
For years, we've been forced to hunt and scavenge for our next meal.
多年来 我们被迫打猎 且为我们的下一顿饭伤脑筋

414
00:25:21,700 --> 00:25:26,500
Well, no more, thanks to our new lucky charm here.
嗯 今后不再这样了 感谢我们这位吉祥物

415
00:25:26,570 --> 00:25:28,660
Hey! Go on, Essie!
喂! 继续 埃西!

416
00:25:28,740 --> 00:25:33,730
I have had an idea that will change our lives.
我已经有一种想法 那将改变我们的生活

417
00:25:33,810 --> 00:25:37,180
We're going to Santa's Fell.
我们要去耶诞老人之家

418
00:25:38,550 --> 00:25:41,950
And we're going to feast on his flying reindeer.
我们他的驯鹿吃掉

419
00:25:44,090 --> 00:25:47,220
And by eating our enemies,
吃掉我们的敌人

420
00:25:47,290 --> 00:25:50,990
their strength will become ours.
他们的团队将成为我们的

421
00:25:52,000 --> 00:25:57,160
You will be Santa's Flying Wolves.
你将是耶诞老人的飞狼队了

422
00:26:00,300 --> 00:26:01,100
Ahem.
啊

423
00:26:01,170 --> 00:26:02,300
Um...
嗯...

424
00:26:02,370 --> 00:26:04,900
maybe I'm barking up the wrong tree,
或许我不该说这样的话

425
00:26:04,980 --> 00:26:09,000
but if you eat Santa's reindeer,
但是如果你吃耶诞老人的驯鹿

426
00:26:09,080 --> 00:26:11,600
don't you think he might just be a little bit upset?
你不认为他有 一点难过吗?

427
00:26:11,680 --> 00:26:12,840
True.
也对

428
00:26:14,420 --> 00:26:17,950
That's why we're going to eat Santa too!
所以我们把耶诞老人也吃掉!

429
00:26:23,860 --> 00:26:27,130
And I'll take his place.
我将取代他的位置

430
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:31,360
Just think of all the delicious little boys and girls
请想起那些美味的小男孩和女孩

431
00:26:31,440 --> 00:26:34,430
waiting for me to visit.
等我去拜访

432
00:26:34,510 --> 00:26:38,530
But... but Santa's supposed to give children presents,
但是... 但是耶诞老人应该 给小孩礼物

433
00:26:38,610 --> 00:26:40,010
not eat them!
而不是吃他们!

434
00:26:40,080 --> 00:26:43,140
New Santa, new rules.
新耶诞老人 新规矩

435
00:26:43,210 --> 00:26:46,380
Next stop, Santa's Fell.
下一站 耶诞老人家

436
00:26:50,090 --> 00:26:51,450
- Huh?  - Huh?
- 嗯?  - 嗯?

437
00:26:51,520 --> 00:26:53,110
I was just leaving!
我正要离开呢!

438
00:26:53,190 --> 00:26:54,710
Get him!
抓住他!

439
00:26:54,790 --> 00:26:56,950
Aaahhh!
啊!

440
00:27:00,300 --> 00:27:02,200
Niko!
尼科!

441
00:27:02,270 --> 00:27:04,460
Niko!
尼科!

442
00:27:04,540 --> 00:27:07,000
Where are you?
你在那里?

443
00:27:07,770 --> 00:27:09,000
Huh?
蛤?

444
00:27:09,070 --> 00:27:12,300
Niko! Boy, am I glad to see you!
尼科! 哎哟 看见你真高兴!

445
00:27:12,380 --> 00:27:13,810
Whoaaa!
哇!

446
00:27:13,880 --> 00:27:17,310
Can't I leave you alone for five minutes?
我离开你 1分钟你就闯祸了?

447
00:27:17,380 --> 00:27:19,180
They're gaining on us!
他们在追我们!

448
00:27:19,250 --> 00:27:20,980
Faster, Niko!
快点 尼科!

449
00:27:21,050 --> 00:27:22,180
You fly!
你飞走!

450
00:27:22,250 --> 00:27:25,020
- Save yourself!  - I'm not leaving you alone again.
- 自己逃命去!  - 我不会再丢下你了

451
00:27:25,090 --> 00:27:26,920
You only make things worse!
你只会给我添麻烦!

452
00:27:40,970 --> 00:27:44,070
- Oh, no!  - Uh-oh!
- 噢 不!  - 噢噢!

453
00:27:48,450 --> 00:27:51,180
The reindeer knows too much.
这支驯鹿知道太多了

454
00:27:52,450 --> 00:27:55,080
No survivors.
别留活口

455
00:28:00,960 --> 00:28:03,620
- My public!  - What?!
- 大家!  - 什么?!

456
00:28:03,690 --> 00:28:04,250
Hmm?
嗯?

457
00:28:04,330 --> 00:28:08,090
My first number is guaranteed to bring the house down.
我保证会让全场 博得满堂喝采

458
00:28:08,170 --> 00:28:12,070
# Well, there's something that I want to say #
# 好的 有些事情 我想要说 #

459
00:28:12,140 --> 00:28:16,400
# And there's something that I've got to do #
# 有某事情 我必须做 #

460
00:28:16,470 --> 00:28:18,340
Oh, goodie! I love a good knees-up!
噢 好呀! 我好爱活跃演唱会!

461
00:28:18,410 --> 00:28:20,310
Really? Me too.
真的吗? 我也是

462
00:28:20,380 --> 00:28:23,510
Oh. This seat's free, miss.
噢 这个位子没人 小姐

463
00:28:25,480 --> 00:28:28,540
# Even got down on my knees to pray #
# 甚至让我下跪祈祷 #

464
00:28:28,620 --> 00:28:31,490
# 'Cause, baby, I miss you #
# 因为 宝贝 我想念你 #

465
00:28:31,660 --> 00:28:34,220
# 'Cause, baby, I miss you #
# 因为 宝贝 我想念你 #

466
00:28:34,290 --> 00:28:36,590
# Whoo! #
# 喔! #

467
00:28:45,200 --> 00:28:45,960
Oh!
噢!

468
00:28:54,550 --> 00:28:56,240
Whoo! Whoa!
喔! 哼!

469
00:28:58,380 --> 00:29:00,210
I'll drive, old-timer!
我来驾驶 老头!

470
00:29:00,280 --> 00:29:02,620
Jump high, reindeer boy!
跳起来 小驯鹿!

471
00:29:04,490 --> 00:29:07,290
# Dah dah doo-dah doo-dah doo-dah whoo! #
# 哒 哒 哒 哒! #

472
00:29:17,440 --> 00:29:18,930
Aaahhhh!
啊啊!

473
00:29:21,770 --> 00:29:24,970
Aaaahhhhhhh!
啊啊!

474
00:29:37,460 --> 00:29:40,320
Ohh! The tree!
噢! 树!

475
00:29:40,390 --> 00:29:42,120
Watch out for the tree!
留意树!

476
00:29:42,860 --> 00:29:46,730
I see it! Backseat drivers!
我看见它了! 后座司机!

477
00:29:46,800 --> 00:29:47,890
Whoa!
喔!

478
00:29:52,100 --> 00:29:54,590
Whoo! Yeah!
噢! 耶!

479
00:29:57,110 --> 00:29:59,510
Oh, here we go!
噢 开始了!

480
00:30:01,980 --> 00:30:05,710
Ohhh!
噢!

481
00:30:05,780 --> 00:30:07,840
Whoo-hoo!
喔吼!

482
00:30:12,920 --> 00:30:15,080
Whoo whoo whoo whoo!
喔 喔 喔 喔!

483
00:30:16,590 --> 00:30:18,320
Huh. Whew!
啊  哎呀!

484
00:30:18,400 --> 00:30:22,360
I can't believe I got out of that without a single scratch.
真不敢相信 我逃出来了

485
00:30:22,430 --> 00:30:23,660
Oh!
噢!

486
00:30:25,700 --> 00:30:27,530
Nice going, Nutboy!
做的好 松果男孩!

487
00:30:27,610 --> 00:30:29,440
Nutboy?
松果男孩?

488
00:30:35,910 --> 00:30:39,350
Aah! My legs! I can't feel my legs!
啊! 我的腿! 我的腿没感觉了!

489
00:30:40,950 --> 00:30:43,010
What the heck are you doing?
你到底在做什么?

490
00:30:43,090 --> 00:30:44,780
All right, sorry!
喔 抱歉!

491
00:30:44,860 --> 00:30:46,350
Keep your hair on!
你的毛还是那么帅!

492
00:30:49,590 --> 00:30:53,120
The reindeer boy must be destroyed!
我一定要杀了那支小驯鹿!

493
00:30:55,570 --> 00:30:57,030
Uh-uh!
噢噢!

494
00:30:57,100 --> 00:31:00,260
Only room for one up here, missy!
只够一个人坐这里 小姐!

495
00:31:00,340 --> 00:31:03,600
Is that the gratitude I get for saving your furry hide?
这就是救了你这多毛的 报答吗?

496
00:31:03,670 --> 00:31:06,730
What do you mean, saving my handsome hide?
你意思是什 就了多帅的我?

497
00:31:06,810 --> 00:31:09,750
I had the situation perfectly under control.
当时情势完全在我控制下

498
00:31:09,810 --> 00:31:12,910
Well, that's the last time I'll save your...
好吧 那是我最后一次救你...

499
00:31:12,980 --> 00:31:16,710
Hey! I said "furry," not "handsome."
喂! 我说"多毛" 不是"多帅"

500
00:31:16,790 --> 00:31:20,220
Okay. So you saved our lives, and now we're quits.
好吧那你救了我们 现在我们扯平

501
00:31:20,290 --> 00:31:22,090
I suppose you'll want to be on your way now.
我认为你现在想一个人 呆着吧

502
00:31:22,160 --> 00:31:23,460
Huh!
哼!

503
00:31:23,530 --> 00:31:25,190
You don't have to go.
你不必走的

504
00:31:25,260 --> 00:31:27,160
I know when I'm not wanted.
我知道你们不需要我了

505
00:31:27,230 --> 00:31:30,460
Let's go, Niko. Santa's Fell is that way.
尼科 让我们去 耶诞老人之家要往这边走

506
00:31:30,530 --> 00:31:34,270
Oh, and before I go, Santa's Fell is that way.
噢 在我走之前 耶诞老人之家是要往这边走

507
00:31:34,340 --> 00:31:37,670
Hey! Don't listen to her. She's totally unreliable.
喂! 不要听她 她可靠不住

508
00:31:37,740 --> 00:31:40,400
- You know the way to Santa's Fell?  - Yep.
- 你知道耶诞老人家的路吗?  - 是

509
00:31:40,480 --> 00:31:42,140
- Used to work there.  - Wow.
- 过去常常在那里工作  - 哇

510
00:31:42,210 --> 00:31:43,610
Did you hear that, Julius?
你听到那了吗 朱利尔斯?

511
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:45,480
You really think we believe that?
你真认为我们会相信吗?

512
00:31:45,550 --> 00:31:46,480
Hmph.
嗯

513
00:31:46,550 --> 00:31:48,450
You gotta come with us.
你必须与我们一起来

514
00:31:48,520 --> 00:31:51,580
The wolves are going to eat Santa and his Flying Forces!
那群野狼打算吃 耶诞老人和他的飞行团队!

515
00:31:51,660 --> 00:31:54,420
What?! When... when were you going to tell me this?
什么?! 你打算... 什么时候 告诉我这事?

516
00:31:54,490 --> 00:31:59,120
Calm down. No wolf ever made it all the way up to Santa's Fell.
冷静点没有野狼可到耶诞老人的家

517
00:32:00,260 --> 00:32:02,130
- Ciao, boys.  - Please!
- 再见 男孩  - 拜托!

518
00:32:02,200 --> 00:32:04,720
We need you! We'll do anything!
我们需要你! 你要我们做任何事都行!

519
00:32:04,800 --> 00:32:05,930
Huh?
嗯?

520
00:32:06,600 --> 00:32:08,270
Anything?
任何事情吗?

521
00:32:12,840 --> 00:32:15,140
Don't get used to the view, missy.
小姐 别习惯看风景

522
00:32:15,210 --> 00:32:18,150
This is strictly a temporary situation.
这只是暂时情势

523
00:32:19,980 --> 00:32:23,750
So... have you ever met the Flying Forces?
因此... 你有见过 飞行团队吗?

524
00:32:23,820 --> 00:32:25,580
Oh, yeah, lots of times.
噢 是 许多次

525
00:32:25,660 --> 00:32:28,060
- Whoa!  - Whoa!
- 哇!  - 哇!

526
00:32:29,730 --> 00:32:32,890
Can't you keep your hands off me for one second?
你可不可别碰我一秒?

527
00:32:32,960 --> 00:32:34,830
Madam, please!
夫人 拜托!

528
00:32:34,900 --> 00:32:36,530
My dad's in the Flying Forces!
我爸爸在飞行团队中!

529
00:32:36,600 --> 00:32:37,900
Maybe you've met him.
或许你已经见过他

530
00:32:37,970 --> 00:32:41,200
Really? Your dad's one of those guys?
真的吗? 你的爸爸 在那些人之中?

531
00:32:41,270 --> 00:32:42,530
Uh-huh.
嗯哼

532
00:32:42,610 --> 00:32:45,470
What do you mean, "one of those guys"?
你意思是什么 在那些人之中?

533
00:32:45,540 --> 00:32:47,410
Oh, n-nothing.
噢 没有什么

534
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:51,180
I just never thought of them as the daddy types.
只不过我未想过他们 也会当爸爸

535
00:32:51,250 --> 00:32:53,840
- What's your dad's name?  - I don't know yet...
- 你的爸爸的名字是什么?  - 我还不知道...

536
00:32:53,920 --> 00:32:56,480
...but he's going to teach me how to fly.
...但是他会教我 怎样飞

537
00:32:56,550 --> 00:32:58,450
Oh, they love their flying.
噢 他们喜爱飞行

538
00:32:58,520 --> 00:33:00,460
It seems like that's all they do.
好像是他们能做的事情

539
00:33:00,520 --> 00:33:04,980
I've taught Niko all the flying exercises he needs to know.
我已经教过尼科 所有飞行需要的练习

540
00:33:05,060 --> 00:33:09,590
Really? Have you taught him launching leaps? Hmm?
真的吗? 你有教他 起飞跳跃吗? 嗯?

541
00:33:09,670 --> 00:33:12,470
Or breathing short bursts?
或是瞬间短冲?

542
00:33:12,540 --> 00:33:15,730
Or using hooves for improved aerodynamics?
或者使用蹄子 使空气产生动力?

543
00:33:15,810 --> 00:33:18,800
Wow! Real flying exercises!
哇! 真正的飞行练习!

544
00:33:20,080 --> 00:33:23,210
I'll be keeping an eye on you, missy.
我会盯注你的 小姐

545
00:33:23,280 --> 00:33:24,540
Really?
真的吗?

546
00:33:24,620 --> 00:33:27,640
Will you, now, Julius? Hmm?
是吗 现在 朱利尔斯? 嗯?

547
00:33:27,720 --> 00:33:29,080
No!
不!

548
00:33:29,150 --> 00:33:31,520
And the name's Nutboy! I mean Julius!
我的名字是松果男孩! 我意思是朱利尔斯!

549
00:33:31,590 --> 00:33:33,150
I mean!
我意思是!

550
00:33:33,220 --> 00:33:35,020
Oh, shut up!
噢 闭嘴!

551
00:33:37,600 --> 00:33:38,820
Wolves!
野狼!

552
00:33:56,780 --> 00:33:59,270
Isn't there a faster way, Wilma?
这是捷径吗 威尔玛?

553
00:33:59,350 --> 00:34:02,290
Well, the shortcut across the River of Certain Doom
嗯 这是通过审判河的捷径

554
00:34:02,350 --> 00:34:04,410
is just around the corner.
就在拐弯那边

555
00:34:04,490 --> 00:34:06,220
River of Certain Doom?!
审判河?!

556
00:34:17,840 --> 00:34:20,000
Okay, this is it!
好 就是它!

557
00:34:20,070 --> 00:34:22,160
That's nothing!
什么也没有啊!

558
00:34:22,240 --> 00:34:24,260
Okay, here's the plan.
好 计划是这样

559
00:34:27,010 --> 00:34:28,240
Run!
跑!

560
00:34:29,650 --> 00:34:31,810
- Hurry, men!  - That's it, Niko! Jump!
- 老兄 赶快!  - 尼科! 跳!

561
00:34:34,720 --> 00:34:36,650
Aah! Aahhh...
啊! 啊啊...

562
00:34:36,720 --> 00:34:39,850
Go for it! Come on! That's it, Niko. You can do it!
跟我来! 那是它 尼科你能做到的!

563
00:34:47,160 --> 00:34:48,830
Nice going, Niko...
做的好 尼科...

564
00:34:48,900 --> 00:34:51,300
and a heck of a plan, Julius.
让你的计画见鬼去吧 朱利尔斯

565
00:34:51,370 --> 00:34:55,100
The River of Certain Doom was a piece of cake.
审判河只是一块蛋糕

566
00:34:55,170 --> 00:34:57,200
That was the Trickle of Tranquility.
那是一条平静的小河

567
00:34:58,680 --> 00:35:01,340
This is the River of Certain Doom.
这 河确信毁灭

568
00:35:06,180 --> 00:35:07,280
How...
怎样...

569
00:35:07,350 --> 00:35:09,250
how do we get across?
我们怎样通过?

570
00:35:09,320 --> 00:35:11,980
Across the bridge, of course.
穿过桥 当然

571
00:35:19,060 --> 00:35:20,690
Or not.
否则

572
00:35:22,870 --> 00:35:25,700
All aboard! We have to fly across!
各位 都上来啦! 我们必须飞过去!

573
00:35:25,770 --> 00:35:27,070
Are you nuts?
你脑壳坏啦?

574
00:35:27,140 --> 00:35:29,400
I'll do the flying exercises Wilma taught me.
我会按照威尔玛教我的 飞行锻链

575
00:35:30,270 --> 00:35:34,140
What's all this Wilma stuff? Don't you listen to me anymore?
威尔玛教你什么? 你没再听我吗?

576
00:35:35,110 --> 00:35:38,080
I do, Julius! You always say I can fly.
我听 朱利尔斯! 你总是说我能飞

577
00:35:38,150 --> 00:35:41,240
That's different! This is for real!
那不同! 这是真的!

578
00:35:42,290 --> 00:35:43,750
Aaah!
啊!

579
00:35:49,290 --> 00:35:51,160
I can fly! I can fly!
我能飞! 我能飞了!

580
00:35:51,230 --> 00:35:54,250
It's working! It's working! It's...!
成功了! 成功了! 成...!

581
00:35:55,500 --> 00:35:59,370
Oh nooooooo!
噢 不!

582
00:35:59,440 --> 00:36:02,130
That's the end of reindeer boy.
小驯鹿玩完了

583
00:36:02,210 --> 00:36:06,070
Looks like you bring us luck after all, marshmallow.
看起来你还是为我们带来好运 小软糖

584
00:36:07,780 --> 00:36:09,080
Poor kid.
不幸的孩子

585
00:36:09,150 --> 00:36:12,380
Come on. We have to find another way across.
跟我来 我们必须找到过去的路

586
00:36:12,450 --> 00:36:16,350
There's a meal waiting at Santa's Fell.
耶诞老人的家 有一顿美食等着我们

587
00:36:16,420 --> 00:36:18,010
Aaaahhhh!
啊!

588
00:36:20,020 --> 00:36:23,720
Whoooaaaa!
哇!

589
00:36:26,300 --> 00:36:28,130
Niko, get up!
尼科 起来!

590
00:36:28,200 --> 00:36:29,360
Hurry!
赶快!

591
00:36:29,430 --> 00:36:31,260
Oh, no! Look!
噢 不! 看!

592
00:36:41,280 --> 00:36:44,650
Niko! Niko! Can you hear me? Ohh!
尼科! 尼科! 你能听到我吗? 哦!

593
00:36:49,250 --> 00:36:50,950
Hurry, Julius, hurry!
赶快 朱利尔斯 赶快!

594
00:36:51,020 --> 00:36:55,080
Uh, right! Rocks! We're going to need rocks!
噢 对了! 岩石! 我们需要岩石!

595
00:36:55,160 --> 00:36:56,790
No! Too big! Too small!
不! 太大! 太小!

596
00:36:56,860 --> 00:36:59,890
Niko's in mortal danger, and you're insulting rocks?
尼科有生命危险 你还在挑剔石头吗?

597
00:37:02,270 --> 00:37:03,930
On my signal...
听我指挥...

598
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:06,230
three, two, one.
三 二 一

599
00:37:06,300 --> 00:37:07,500
Now!
现在发射!

600
00:37:14,850 --> 00:37:16,470
Niko!
尼科!

601
00:37:17,310 --> 00:37:19,040
Niko! Niko!
尼科! 尼科!

602
00:37:26,160 --> 00:37:28,060
- Oh!  - Unh.
- 噢!  - 啊

603
00:37:58,090 --> 00:37:59,490
No!
不!

604
00:37:59,560 --> 00:38:01,220
No!
不!

605
00:38:09,900 --> 00:38:10,890
Oh oh oh!
噢 噢噢!

606
00:38:10,970 --> 00:38:14,340
He's alive! He's alive!
他活着! 他活着!

607
00:38:16,240 --> 00:38:17,500
Oh.
噢

608
00:38:19,440 --> 00:38:21,000
Nice work, Nutboy.
干得好 松果男孩

609
00:38:21,080 --> 00:38:23,710
Uh, you too. Whatever.
噢 你也是随你怎么说吧

610
00:38:23,780 --> 00:38:27,840
Come on. We can't just lie around here all day.
跟我来 我们不能整天躺在这

611
00:38:31,920 --> 00:38:35,380
I think somebody does need to lie around here all day.
我认为某人确实需要 整天躺在这

612
00:38:46,740 --> 00:38:47,970
Specs?
史贝斯?

613
00:38:48,110 --> 00:38:49,370
Huh?
嗯?

614
00:38:49,440 --> 00:38:53,840
Do you really think Black Wolf will eat Santa and his Flying Forces?
你真的认为布莱克黑狼 将吃耶诞老人和他的飞行团队吗?

615
00:38:53,910 --> 00:38:55,880
Well, you know,
嗯 你知道

616
00:38:55,950 --> 00:38:59,640
doing bad things is kind of a tradition for us wolves.
做坏事对我们野狼来说 是一种传统

617
00:39:01,080 --> 00:39:03,380
But we're not all like that... nasty, I mean.
但是我们一点也不象那样... 肮脏 我意思是

618
00:39:03,450 --> 00:39:05,750
Some of us just look that way.
我们中有一些人看起来像坏蛋

619
00:39:05,820 --> 00:39:10,050
Hey, do you think you could make me look like less of a bad guy?
喂 你觉得有办法让我 看起来不像一个坏蛋吗?

620
00:39:10,130 --> 00:39:12,030
Hmm, let's see.
噢 让我想想

621
00:39:13,330 --> 00:39:15,800
You can start by wagging your tail.
你可以从摇尾巴开始

622
00:39:15,870 --> 00:39:17,030
Okay.
好吧

623
00:39:20,340 --> 00:39:21,770
Come on, tail!
加油 尾巴!

624
00:39:23,140 --> 00:39:24,400
Wag!
摇摇!

625
00:39:25,780 --> 00:39:28,210
Talking to your tail again, Specs?
又再对你的尾巴说话了 史贝斯?

626
00:39:28,280 --> 00:39:29,400
Huh?
嗯?

627
00:39:47,200 --> 00:39:48,320
Oh!
噢!

628
00:39:52,800 --> 00:39:55,530
Hey, Nutboy! Who are your friends?
喂 松果男孩! 你的朋友是谁?

629
00:39:55,610 --> 00:39:57,340
Oh... nobody.
噢... 没人

630
00:39:57,410 --> 00:39:59,500
Aren't you going to introduce me?
你不打算把我 介绍给大家吗?

631
00:39:59,580 --> 00:40:00,810
Well...
好...

632
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:02,810
that's my Aunt Sally
那是我的姑母萨莉

633
00:40:02,880 --> 00:40:05,870
and that's my wife and that's...
那是我的妻子 那是...

634
00:40:05,950 --> 00:40:08,210
that's my son.
那是我的儿子

635
00:40:08,290 --> 00:40:10,150
Why aren't you at home with them
为什么你不在家陪他们

636
00:40:10,220 --> 00:40:12,920
instead of hanging around with reindeer boy?
而是跟驯鹿小孩在这?

637
00:40:12,990 --> 00:40:16,020
One time long ago...
很久以前...

638
00:40:16,090 --> 00:40:21,530
it... it was a cold winter, and the little one was hungry,
那... 那是一个寒冬 我儿子饿了

639
00:40:21,600 --> 00:40:24,800
so I went out to find food.
因此我出去找点食物

640
00:40:24,870 --> 00:40:28,970
When I came back, they were all gone...
当我回来时 他们全部不见了...

641
00:40:29,040 --> 00:40:33,200
Aunt Sally, my wife, my son.
萨莉姑母 我的妻子 我的孩子

642
00:40:34,780 --> 00:40:36,470
In the snow were tracks.
在雪里有脚印

643
00:40:37,520 --> 00:40:38,850
Wolf tracks.
野狼脚印

644
00:40:39,850 --> 00:40:42,610
Oh, I'm so sorry, Nutboy.
噢 我非常抱歉 松果男孩

645
00:40:42,690 --> 00:40:44,620
I... I didn't know.
我... 我不知道是这样

646
00:40:44,690 --> 00:40:46,490
Niko's my family now...
现在尼科是我的家人...

647
00:40:47,430 --> 00:40:50,050
at least until he finds his real dad.
至少直到他找到 他真正的爸爸

648
00:40:51,700 --> 00:40:53,160
What about you?
你怎么样?

649
00:40:53,230 --> 00:40:54,700
Do you have a family?
你有家人吗?

650
00:40:54,770 --> 00:40:56,890
Yeah, sort of.
是的 算是有

651
00:40:56,970 --> 00:40:58,200
Sort of?
算是有?

652
00:40:58,270 --> 00:40:59,960
Truth is,
事实是

653
00:41:00,040 --> 00:41:02,560
my family didn't want me to be a singer,
我的家人不想要我 成为一位歌手

654
00:41:02,640 --> 00:41:05,070
but I was young and restless,
但是我那时年轻气盛

655
00:41:05,140 --> 00:41:07,630
so, uh, I ran away from home.
因此 噢 我离家出走

656
00:41:08,680 --> 00:41:10,370
I've been away for years.
我离家出走多年了

657
00:41:10,450 --> 00:41:12,940
I know what it's like
我知道那种感觉

658
00:41:13,020 --> 00:41:14,480
to be on your own.
凡事都得靠自己

659
00:41:22,560 --> 00:41:23,750
Huh?
啊?

660
00:41:23,830 --> 00:41:25,390
I had a dream.
我有做个梦

661
00:41:25,460 --> 00:41:29,460
I dreamt that Black Wolf attacked the herd and ate Mom...
我梦见那匹布莱克野狼 攻击鹿群且把妈妈吃掉了...

662
00:41:29,530 --> 00:41:31,230
and Saga.
以及传说

663
00:41:31,300 --> 00:41:34,140
It's just a nightmare, Niko.
它只是个恶梦 尼科

664
00:41:34,210 --> 00:41:37,700
It wasn't your fault the wolves attacked the herd.
野狼攻击鹿群这不是你的错

665
00:41:37,780 --> 00:41:39,470
Nobody blames you.
没人责备你

666
00:41:39,540 --> 00:41:41,010
How do you know?
你怎样知道?

667
00:41:41,080 --> 00:41:44,240
If Julius says so, then it's true.
如果朱利尔斯这样说 那么它就是真的

668
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:45,610
Huh?
啊?

669
00:41:51,520 --> 00:41:53,180
Wow!
哇!

670
00:42:12,010 --> 00:42:16,070
# Well, there's something that I want to say #
# 好的 我有某些事想要说 #

671
00:42:16,150 --> 00:42:19,670
# And there's something that I've got to do #
# 和我有某些事必须做 #

672
00:42:20,790 --> 00:42:24,120
# Even got down on my knees to pray #
# 甚至下跪祈祷 #

673
00:42:24,190 --> 00:42:26,180
# 'Cause, baby, I miss you #
# 因为 宝贝 我想念你 #

674
00:42:26,360 --> 00:42:29,050
# 'Cause, baby, I miss you #
# 因为 宝贝 我想念你 #

675
00:42:29,130 --> 00:42:32,690
# Oooohhhh! # Yeah!
哦! 耶!

676
00:42:32,760 --> 00:42:37,790
Gentlemen, I give you... Santa's Fell!
各位先生 让我介绍... 耶诞老人之家!

677
00:42:47,110 --> 00:42:50,640
We did it! Yay!
我们成功了! 哇!

678
00:42:50,710 --> 00:42:53,840
- Whoo-hoo! Whoo!  - Come on!
- 喔! 喔!  - 快来呀!

679
00:42:53,920 --> 00:42:57,980
We have to hurry! It's Christmas Day tomorrow!
我们必须赶快! 明天就是耶诞节!

680
00:43:05,600 --> 00:43:08,590
The entrance to Santa's Fell,
耶诞老人家的入口

681
00:43:08,670 --> 00:43:12,600
said to be haunted and full of deadly traps at every turn.
据说里面鬼魂出没 且处处充满陷阱

682
00:43:12,670 --> 00:43:16,540
No one who has gone in there has made it back out alive.
进入那里的人 没有人活着出来

683
00:43:17,780 --> 00:43:18,760
Cool!
真酷!

684
00:43:18,840 --> 00:43:20,870
Last one in is a chicken!
最后一个是小鸡!

685
00:43:22,680 --> 00:43:24,550
Hey!
喂!

686
00:43:39,960 --> 00:43:41,400
Hey, shh!
喂 嘘!

687
00:43:41,470 --> 00:43:43,960
Here's the secret shortcut.
这是个秘密的捷径

688
00:43:44,030 --> 00:43:45,520
Whoa, whoa.
哇 哇

689
00:43:45,600 --> 00:43:48,440
We haven't been very lucky with shortcuts,
我们从未幸运走过捷径

690
00:43:48,510 --> 00:43:50,910
so in my considered opinion...
因此在我考虑后...

691
00:43:54,110 --> 00:43:56,880
You didn't hear my considered opinion!
你们都没听到我考虑后的想法!

692
00:44:15,830 --> 00:44:18,770
After you, marshmallow.
你先请 小软糖

693
00:44:20,570 --> 00:44:22,100
Ohh!
哦!

694
00:44:22,170 --> 00:44:24,110
But... I thought I was your lucky charm.
但是... 我以为我是你的幸运符

695
00:44:24,170 --> 00:44:25,230
You are.
你是

696
00:44:25,310 --> 00:44:28,840
If there are any surprises in there,
如果那里有任何惊奇

697
00:44:28,910 --> 00:44:30,970
you get them first.
你会第一个得到

698
00:44:32,180 --> 00:44:33,410
Lucky for us!
为我们带个好运!

699
00:44:33,480 --> 00:44:36,010
I'll go first, boss.
我先走 头家

700
00:44:36,090 --> 00:44:37,080
Huh?
嗯?

701
00:44:37,790 --> 00:44:41,020
I'm going to miss you, Specs.
我会想念你 史贝斯

702
00:44:57,340 --> 00:44:59,610
Watch the step, guys.
小伙子 小心

703
00:45:06,080 --> 00:45:07,550
That's it!
够了!

704
00:45:07,620 --> 00:45:11,210
Niko, I'm not letting you go one step further.
尼科 我不让你再踏台阶了

705
00:45:11,290 --> 00:45:12,810
You go on, Wilma.
你继续 威尔玛

706
00:45:12,890 --> 00:45:16,120
Find his dad and tell him the boy says hello.
找到他的爸爸告诉他 他儿子向他问好

707
00:45:16,190 --> 00:45:18,920
Niko and me will stay right here.
尼科和我就留在这里

708
00:45:33,210 --> 00:45:36,770
Nothing to be afraid of. Ice can't hurt me.
没有什么害怕 冰不能伤害我

709
00:45:36,850 --> 00:45:38,710
Ice is nice.
冰是好的

710
00:45:39,780 --> 00:45:41,220
Nice ice.
好的冰

711
00:45:41,290 --> 00:45:42,650
Move it.
移动它

712
00:45:48,760 --> 00:45:51,250
Oh! Unh! Ohh!
噢! 啊! 啊!

713
00:45:51,330 --> 00:45:52,590
Aah!
啊!

714
00:45:58,340 --> 00:46:00,170
Specs!
史贝斯!

715
00:46:00,240 --> 00:46:01,670
Look out!
小心!

716
00:46:06,810 --> 00:46:09,210
Thanks.
感谢

717
00:46:15,090 --> 00:46:16,070
Uhn!
嗯!

718
00:46:16,150 --> 00:46:17,850
Boys.
男孩

719
00:46:17,920 --> 00:46:22,920
This is it... the place where dreams come true.
这里... 就是梦想实现的地方

720
00:46:26,630 --> 00:46:27,860
Wow.
哇

721
00:46:28,570 --> 00:46:31,400
Up there is Santa's factory.
上面就是耶诞老人的工厂了

722
00:46:31,470 --> 00:46:33,060
Look at that!
看那!

723
00:46:33,140 --> 00:46:36,700
And that's the Flying Forces airport.
那就是飞行团队的机场

724
00:46:36,770 --> 00:46:37,900
Wow.
哇

725
00:46:41,980 --> 00:46:45,240
Dad! I'm gonna meet Dad!
爸爸! 我将要见到爸爸!

726
00:46:45,320 --> 00:46:47,280
You know, Niko,
你知道 尼科

727
00:46:47,350 --> 00:46:51,650
people aren't always exactly the way you think they are.
人们不总是 正好是想的那样

728
00:46:51,720 --> 00:46:55,420
I know exactly what Dad is... a hero!
我确切知道爸爸是什么... 一名英雄!

729
00:46:55,490 --> 00:46:56,690
No, but he...
不 但是他...

730
00:46:56,760 --> 00:46:59,750
What Nutboy's trying to say is, well...
松果男孩想说的是 嗯...

731
00:46:59,830 --> 00:47:03,990
Sometimes heroes turn out to be just like everyone else.
有时英雄正如其他人一样

732
00:47:04,070 --> 00:47:06,130
My dad's not like everyone else.
我的爸爸和别人不一样

733
00:47:09,510 --> 00:47:12,600
Maybe we should come back after Christmas!
或许我们应该在耶诞节之后回来!

734
00:47:12,680 --> 00:47:15,080
- Niko!  - Ohh...
- 尼科!  - 哦...

735
00:47:15,150 --> 00:47:16,840
Wait.
等一下

736
00:47:28,230 --> 00:47:29,920
Wow!
哇!

737
00:47:29,990 --> 00:47:32,460
Stay sharp, men.
保持敏锐 老兄

738
00:47:32,530 --> 00:47:34,430
Christmas is no time for fun.
耶诞节可没时间开玩笑

739
00:47:34,500 --> 00:47:36,930
Well, it is, but you know what I mean.
嗯 是的 但是你们知道我的意思

740
00:47:37,000 --> 00:47:37,990
Uh, Dasher...
噢 气宇轩昂...

741
00:47:38,070 --> 00:47:40,300
I'm not in the mood for interruptions, Comet.
我不想要被打搅 彗星来说

742
00:47:40,370 --> 00:47:41,840
- But Dasher!  - You too, Blitzen.
