# Have a happy, happy... #
# 快乐的 快乐的... #

912
00:58:51,210 --> 00:58:53,680
Help! Santa! The wolves are here!
救命! 耶诞老人! 野狼在这里!

913
00:58:53,740 --> 00:58:55,640
You've reached Santa's Hotline.
你已经拨通耶诞老人的热线

914
00:58:55,710 --> 00:58:58,980
If you've been nice all year and want to leave a wish list,
如果你一年都乖乖的 那么

915
00:58:59,050 --> 00:59:00,950
please press one.
就许个愿吧

916
00:59:01,020 --> 00:59:02,380
If you've been naughty,
如果你顽皮

917
00:59:02,450 --> 00:59:06,980
please hold and one of our elf operators will be with you shortly.
那么我们的小精灵 马上就会接你的电话

918
00:59:12,530 --> 00:59:15,520
Please state the nature of your naughtiness.
说说你为何顽皮

919
00:59:16,870 --> 00:59:18,930
Oh... kay.
噢... 嗯

920
00:59:19,000 --> 00:59:21,400
No presents for you this year.
你今年收不到礼物了

921
00:59:21,470 --> 00:59:22,960
Rrrraaaahhhh!
啊啊!

922
00:59:59,440 --> 01:00:02,570
- Wow, a teddy bear!  - Wow!
- 哇 一头玩具熊!  - 哇!

923
01:00:02,650 --> 01:00:03,770
Lucky you!
你真走运!

924
01:00:09,350 --> 01:00:11,480
Hey, reindeer boy.
喂 小驯鹿

925
01:00:11,560 --> 01:00:14,720
Know how we catch squirrels in the summer?
知道我们夏天怎样抓住松鼠吗?

926
01:00:17,860 --> 01:00:19,520
Aah!
啊!

927
01:00:19,600 --> 01:00:22,570
Leave him alone!
住手!

928
01:00:22,630 --> 01:00:25,470
Don't worry, Niko! I'll take care of him.
不要担心! 尼科 我来搞定他

929
01:00:32,540 --> 01:00:34,310
Aaahhhh!
啊啊!

930
01:00:34,380 --> 01:00:35,400
Julius!
朱利尔斯!

931
01:00:36,880 --> 01:00:38,040
Ohh!
哦!

932
01:00:46,820 --> 01:00:48,920
- Niko!  - Just relax, Prancer.
- 尼科!  - 放松点 烈马

933
01:00:48,990 --> 01:00:50,860
- This is good, this is good.  - Come on!
- 很好 很好  - 拜托!

934
01:00:50,930 --> 01:00:52,990
- Your face is fine...  - You gotta help him!
- 你很帅...  - 你必须帮助他!

935
01:00:53,060 --> 01:00:54,430
You can fly!
你能飞!

936
01:00:54,500 --> 01:00:57,090
I can't see them... so they can't see me.
我不能看见他们... 因此他们不能看见我

937
01:01:02,510 --> 01:01:04,300
Oh, grr!
噢 额!

938
01:01:04,370 --> 01:01:07,970
No one to help you now, reindeer boy!
没有人现在帮助你 小驯鹿!

939
01:01:08,040 --> 01:01:09,510
Huh?
嗯?

940
01:01:12,080 --> 01:01:13,340
Whoooaaaa!
哇!

941
01:01:14,550 --> 01:01:15,070
Huh?
阿?

942
01:01:30,770 --> 01:01:34,760
Hey, come back here, you coward! I wasn't finished.
喂 回到这 你这个懦夫! 我还没玩完

943
01:01:43,280 --> 01:01:44,470
Oompf!
喔!

944
01:01:46,420 --> 01:01:47,310
Oohhh!
噢啊!

945
01:01:48,050 --> 01:01:48,680
Unh!
嗯!

946
01:01:49,390 --> 01:01:51,120
Ooonkh!
噢!

947
01:01:51,190 --> 01:01:54,720
Niko needs help! Save him!
尼科需要帮助! 快去救他!

948
01:01:54,790 --> 01:01:57,390
We... we can't even save ourselves.
我们... 我们甚至不能救自己

949
01:01:57,460 --> 01:02:01,860
That boy braved rivers, wolves, and blizzards to meet you,
那个男孩不怕河 野狼 大风雪 来见你们

950
01:02:01,930 --> 01:02:03,660
the Flying Forces.
飞行团队

951
01:02:03,730 --> 01:02:08,140
He thought you were the bravest, most heroic reindeer in the world.
他认为你是最勇敢的 在世界上的大多数英雄驯鹿

952
01:02:08,210 --> 01:02:09,970
He believed in you!
他那么相信你们!

953
01:02:10,040 --> 01:02:12,870
Well? Was he wrong?
好吗? 他错误吗?

954
01:02:12,940 --> 01:02:15,540
Are you the world famous Flying Forces
你们还是世界闻名的 飞越团队

955
01:02:15,610 --> 01:02:18,270
who never give up, no matter what,
不论发生什么 都从未放弃的 飞鹿吗

956
01:02:18,350 --> 01:02:22,310
or... or just a bunch of frightened... horses?
或者... 或者只不过一群... 害怕吓破胆的马?

957
01:02:22,820 --> 01:02:24,080
Aah!
啊!

958
01:02:41,070 --> 01:02:44,060
We're reindeer, we're not horses.
我们是驯鹿 我们不是马

959
01:02:44,140 --> 01:02:46,230
We're Santa's Flying Forces.
我们是耶诞老人的飞行团队

960
01:02:46,310 --> 01:02:47,710
Ho, ho!
何!

961
01:03:00,420 --> 01:03:02,250
Aah!
啊!

962
01:03:12,700 --> 01:03:15,900
Ha ha ha!
哈哈哈!

963
01:03:17,010 --> 01:03:19,030
Aaaaahhhhhh...
啊啊...

964
01:03:19,110 --> 01:03:20,800
...ooohhh!
...噢!

965
01:03:20,880 --> 01:03:22,280
Niko!
尼科!

966
01:03:22,350 --> 01:03:23,640
Julius!
朱利尔斯!

967
01:03:28,550 --> 01:03:29,540
Aah!
啊!

968
01:03:31,560 --> 01:03:32,750
Hold on, Niko!
尼科 稍等!

969
01:04:04,750 --> 01:04:06,520
Men, Santa Speed!
同志们 耶诞老人速度!

970
01:04:21,970 --> 01:04:25,310
End of the line for you, reindeer boy.
是时候解决你了 小驯鹿

971
01:04:28,480 --> 01:04:30,540
Julius! No!
朱利尔斯! 不!

972
01:04:31,680 --> 01:04:34,710
- I've always believed in you, Niko.  - Aah!
- 我总是相信你 尼科  - 啊!

973
01:04:41,930 --> 01:04:43,690
Julius!
朱利尔斯!

974
01:04:43,760 --> 01:04:46,630
Aaaahhhh!
啊!

975
01:04:52,240 --> 01:04:55,860
At least I won't go on an empty stomach!
至少我不会饿着肚子!

976
01:04:55,940 --> 01:04:57,410
Leave him alone!
放开他!

977
01:05:02,580 --> 01:05:05,950
Rrraaaawwwrrrr!
啊!

978
01:05:07,520 --> 01:05:10,490
You did, it Niko! You can fly!
你做到了 尼科! 你能飞!

979
01:05:10,650 --> 01:05:12,280
You can fly!
你能飞!

980
01:05:12,360 --> 01:05:16,090
Yahoo!
ㄚ呼

981
01:05:34,880 --> 01:05:36,780
Huh?
哈?

982
01:05:49,090 --> 01:05:51,030
Boss...
头家...

983
01:05:53,530 --> 01:05:55,690
What do we do now?
现在我们怎么办?

984
01:05:58,030 --> 01:06:01,940
Who needs reindeer when you've got moss?
当你有苔藓时 谁需要驯鹿?

985
01:06:05,810 --> 01:06:07,780
Rahhh!
啊!

986
01:06:08,850 --> 01:06:10,870
Raahhh! Raahhh!
啊! 啊!

987
01:06:16,290 --> 01:06:21,090
Hey, you wanna go see if there are some leftovers in Santa's kitchen?
喂 你想不想要看看耶诞老人的厨房 是否有一些剩馀物吗?

988
01:06:21,160 --> 01:06:24,650
That sounds like the best Christmas present ever.
那听上去是 最好的耶诞礼物

989
01:06:29,070 --> 01:06:30,620
Hey, kid.
嗨 孩子

990
01:06:30,700 --> 01:06:31,930
Good work.
做的好

991
01:06:32,000 --> 01:06:33,300
Thanks.
谢谢

992
01:06:33,370 --> 01:06:35,300
Uh, Prancer, is it?
噢 烈性的马 是吗?

993
01:06:35,370 --> 01:06:39,930
Well, actually, you can... you can call me...
嗯 实际上 你能... 你能叫我...

994
01:06:41,780 --> 01:06:43,440
...Dad.
...爸爸

995
01:06:43,510 --> 01:06:46,140
- You're... you're my dad?  - Whoa, whoa!
- 你是... 你是我的爸爸吗?  - 嗯 嗯!

996
01:06:46,220 --> 01:06:49,780
Yeah. I... I guess so.
是的 我... 大概是的

997
01:06:49,850 --> 01:06:51,080
Wow.
哇

998
01:06:55,360 --> 01:06:59,520
Hey, fellas, a big cheer for my son, the hero!
喂 伙计们为我的儿子 欢呼吧 小英雄!

999
01:06:59,600 --> 01:07:01,260
Hey!
嗨!

1000
01:07:01,330 --> 01:07:03,820
# For he's a jolly good reindeer #
# 他是非常快乐的小驯鹿 #

1001
01:07:03,900 --> 01:07:05,330
# For he's a jolly good reindeer #
# 他是非常快乐的小驯鹿 #

1002
01:07:05,500 --> 01:07:07,990
# For he's a jolly good reindeer #
# 他是非常快乐的小驯鹿 #

1003
01:07:28,560 --> 01:07:30,620
Nice one, son.
不错 儿子

1004
01:07:31,860 --> 01:07:35,300
Ho, ho, ho, men, Santa's ready!
喉 喉 喉 兄弟们 耶诞老人准备好了!

1005
01:07:55,450 --> 01:07:57,220
Oh, wow!
噢 哇!

1006
01:07:58,960 --> 01:08:02,550
So, you must be Niko.
嗯 你一定是尼科

1007
01:08:02,630 --> 01:08:05,320
Uh, yes, sir.
噢 是的 先生

1008
01:08:05,400 --> 01:08:07,830
I hear you've had quite a time.
我听说你很了不起

1009
01:08:07,900 --> 01:08:09,660
I've had a word with the boys,
我已经和他们谈过了

1010
01:08:09,730 --> 01:08:13,930
and they tell me you may be able to do me a little favor.
他们告诉我你愿意 帮我一点忙

1011
01:08:14,000 --> 01:08:15,530
Huh?
啊?

1012
01:08:26,320 --> 01:08:28,010
Oh, wow.
噢 哇

1013
01:08:49,470 --> 01:08:53,000
Look at the boy. He really did it.
看这孩子 他真的做到了

1014
01:08:54,180 --> 01:08:55,740
Huh.
哎

1015
01:08:57,180 --> 01:08:59,940
You were pretty heroic yourself, Julius.
你相当勇敢阿 朱利尔斯

1016
01:09:01,490 --> 01:09:05,050
I kinda like "Nutboy."
我只是个松果男孩

1017
01:09:08,460 --> 01:09:09,690
Aww.
啊

1018
01:09:19,200 --> 01:09:22,900
Listen, kid, I'm sorry about earlier...
听我说 孩子 很抱歉我应该早点...

1019
01:09:22,970 --> 01:09:25,410
you know, not telling you right away.
你知道 应该早点告诉你

1020
01:09:25,480 --> 01:09:26,910
I guess I was...
我觉得我有点...

1021
01:09:27,980 --> 01:09:29,100
Scared?
害怕吗?

1022
01:09:29,180 --> 01:09:30,810
No. No, no, no.
不 不 不 不

1023
01:09:30,880 --> 01:09:33,820
Santa's reindeer don't get scared.
耶诞老人的驯鹿不害怕的

1024
01:09:33,880 --> 01:09:37,620
When Christmas is over, Dad, we can go back to the herd
爸爸 我想 当耶诞节结束时 我们能回到鹿群

1025
01:09:37,690 --> 01:09:40,620
and you'll meet Mom again... and Grandpa!
并且你将再次见到妈妈... 以及爷爷!

1026
01:09:40,690 --> 01:09:42,680
And we can all live together!
我们能生活在一起了!

1027
01:09:42,760 --> 01:09:46,530
Oh, of course, that'd be just great,
噢 当然 太好了

1028
01:09:46,600 --> 01:09:48,930
but we need to practice flying every day.
但是我们需要每天练飞行

1029
01:09:49,000 --> 01:09:51,660
You know, race over the Alps, shoot up to the moon.
你知道飞行在阿尔卑斯山上方的比赛 飞到月亮

1030
01:09:52,870 --> 01:09:55,170
But what about after all that?
还有呢?

1031
01:09:55,240 --> 01:09:58,070
After all that, we'll have even more fun!
以后所有 我们将有更多的开心!

1032
01:09:58,140 --> 01:10:00,770
Sing reindeer songs, play reindeer games!
唱驯鹿歌 玩法驯鹿比赛!

1033
01:10:00,840 --> 01:10:03,210
And boogie the night away!
以及离开的Boogie夜晚!

1034
01:10:03,280 --> 01:10:04,710
# Unh unh unh unh unh-unh #
# 啊 啊 啊 啊 啊 #

1035
01:10:04,780 --> 01:10:06,540
- Funky!  - Yah, mon.
- 胆战心惊!  - 嗳呀

1036
01:10:18,660 --> 01:10:20,860
I have to go back home now, Niko.
我必须现在回家 尼科

1037
01:10:20,930 --> 01:10:23,020
I'll tell your mother you're all right.
我会告诉你的母亲你们很好

1038
01:10:23,100 --> 01:10:24,160
Huh?
啊?

1039
01:10:24,230 --> 01:10:27,030
I know you'll be the best reindeer on the Flying Forces.
我知道你将是最好的驯鹿 在飞行团队时

1040
01:10:27,100 --> 01:10:28,370
Julius, wait!
朱利尔斯 等等!

1041
01:10:28,440 --> 01:10:30,500
Just like you always dreamed of!
要好好为理想奋斗!

1042
01:10:30,570 --> 01:10:33,370
No, Julius! Come back!
不 朱利尔斯! 回来!

1043
01:10:34,110 --> 01:10:35,940
Goodbye...
再见...

1044
01:10:36,010 --> 01:10:37,380
...son.
...儿子

1045
01:10:39,820 --> 01:10:41,480
No...
不...

1046
01:10:41,550 --> 01:10:43,580
Why did he leave, Wilma?
威尔玛 他为什么离开?

1047
01:10:43,650 --> 01:10:46,350
I have a feeling he didn't want to get in the way.
我有一种感觉 他不想要碍事

1048
01:10:58,940 --> 01:11:00,700
I'm telling the truth!
我正说真话!

1049
01:11:00,770 --> 01:11:04,710
Niko can fly and has joined Santa's Flying Forces!
尼科能飞并且已经参加 耶诞老人的飞行团队!

1050
01:11:04,770 --> 01:11:07,270
We don't have time for your stories, Julius.
我们没有时间 对你的故事来说 朱利尔斯

1051
01:11:07,340 --> 01:11:10,210
They don't put food in our mouths.
我们从未见过他们

1052
01:11:11,520 --> 01:11:15,850
I trusted you to bring my boy back!
我还相信你会带我的孩子回来!

1053
01:11:18,090 --> 01:11:19,250
Uhh.
嗯

1054
01:11:19,320 --> 01:11:21,090
I believe you, Julius.
我相信你 朱利尔斯

1055
01:11:22,130 --> 01:11:24,560
Do you think Niko's happy?
你认为尼科愉快吗?

1056
01:11:24,630 --> 01:11:29,360
Sure. I've never seen him so happy.
当然 我从未看见他如此愉快

1057
01:11:42,210 --> 01:11:44,510
Yeehaw!
耶噢!

1058
01:11:44,580 --> 01:11:45,840
- Hey!  - What?
- 喂!  - 什么?

1059
01:11:45,920 --> 01:11:48,280
What's that up there?
在那里向上的那个是什么?

1060
01:11:48,350 --> 01:11:51,720
- What on earth is that?  - It's Niko!
- 那个究竟是什么?  - 是尼科!

1061
01:11:51,790 --> 01:11:54,050
Wahoo!
啊哈!

1062
01:11:54,120 --> 01:11:55,150
Niko?
尼科吗?

1063
01:11:57,290 --> 01:11:59,990
- Niko can fly!  - Huh?
- 尼科能飞!  - 啊?

1064
01:12:00,060 --> 01:12:02,790
Whoa! Niko can fly!
哇! 尼科能飞!

1065
01:12:14,010 --> 01:12:17,450
Niko! My little boy!
尼科! 我的小男孩!

1066
01:12:18,550 --> 01:12:22,110
Mom! Not in front of everybody.
妈妈! 不要在每人的面前

1067
01:12:22,190 --> 01:12:25,150
What happened? Are you all right?
怎么回事? 你好吗?

1068
01:12:25,220 --> 01:12:27,160
Where have you been!
你到那里了!

1069
01:12:27,220 --> 01:12:30,160
I'm sorry I ran away, Mom.
 妈妈 对不起我跑了

1070
01:12:30,230 --> 01:12:34,190
Niko? Why aren't you with the Flying Forces?
尼科吗? 为什么你没和飞行团队一起?

1071
01:12:34,260 --> 01:12:37,130
Uh, because, well...
噢 因为 好...

1072
01:12:37,200 --> 01:12:40,400
And they let you fly off on your own?
他们让你 独立飞走吗?

1073
01:12:40,470 --> 01:12:44,410
Those irresponsible, good-for-nothing...
那些无责任感的 一无是处...

1074
01:12:44,470 --> 01:12:46,410
# We're Santa's Flying Forces! Ho ho! #
# 我们是耶诞老人的飞行团队 后 后! #

1075
01:12:46,540 --> 01:12:48,100
It's them!
是他们!

1076
01:12:49,810 --> 01:12:52,300
I never thought I'd see the day.
我从未认为我将看见这天

1077
01:12:52,380 --> 01:12:54,650
Make it snappy, boys!
男孩 快点!

1078
01:12:54,720 --> 01:12:57,810
As a token of our gratitude for saving our lives,
为救我们的生命 作为我们报答之恩

1079
01:12:57,890 --> 01:13:00,750
Julius the Flying Squirrel will from now on be
朱利尔斯今后是 飞行松鼠

1080
01:13:00,820 --> 01:13:04,490
an honorary member of Santa's Flying Forces.
也是一名光荣的 耶诞老人的飞行团队

1081
01:13:04,560 --> 01:13:07,190
- What?  - Ja, ja! Excellent!
- 什么?  - 啊 啊! 真好!

1082
01:13:08,770 --> 01:13:10,430
Okay, men, come on!
好 兄弟们 跟我来!

1083
01:13:14,640 --> 01:13:17,040
# He's a squirrel, not a hamster #
# 他是一只松鼠 并非一只仓鼠 #

1084
01:13:17,110 --> 01:13:20,130
# A hero, not a prankster! Ho ho! #
# 一名英雄 并非一个捣蛋鬼! 后 后! #

1085
01:13:20,210 --> 01:13:22,440
Thanks, guys.
小伙子 谢谢

1086
01:13:22,510 --> 01:13:24,710
That's... almost too much.
那是... 太过奖了

1087
01:13:24,780 --> 01:13:28,720
Yes, well, it is, but, what the heck, it's Christmas!
是的 嗯 它 但是 管它呢 今天是耶诞节!

1088
01:13:30,290 --> 01:13:33,480
Hey, Niko, you coming with us?
嗨 尼科你与我们一起来?

1089
01:13:34,190 --> 01:13:38,750
I went all the way to Santa's Fell to find my dad,
我一路走 开始找到我的爸爸 对於耶诞老人来说

1090
01:13:38,830 --> 01:13:42,200
but then I realized he was with me all along.
